Class NewPlayerShipIO

java.lang.Object
io.NewPlayerIO
io.NewPlayerShipIO
public class NewPlayerShipIO
extends NewPlayerIO
The NewPlayerShipIO is a NewPlayerIO sub-class to create a command line interface for setting the ship of the new Trader.

Author:
Finn van Dorsser, Meng Zhang
